      </li>

      <li>
        <h4>CONFIRM ORDER</h4>
        <p>Review the list of items that you have selected to purchase and click "Confirm" to submit your order. An ORDER ID & order details will appear on screen, and you will also receive an email report regarding your order. </p>
      </li>

      <li>
        <h4>CONFIRM PAYMENT</h4>
        <p>When you have completed your payment, re-visit the web to enter your ORDER ID at the confirm payment link. You will receive your payment confirmation via email after you have submitted your payment details.</p>
      </li>

       <li>
